PCase51.hs:(18,15)-(21,9): Splicing expression
    ghc-internal:GHC.Internal.TH.Quote.quoteExp
      pCase
      " e of\n\
      \         _ | isZero e  -> e .== e =: qed\n\
      \           | sTrue     -> e .== e =: qed\n\
      \       "
  ======>
    cases
      [(isZero e ==> (e .== e =: qed)),
       (sNot (isZero e) ==> (e .== e =: qed))]
